---
title: Vietnamese-Style Caramelized Beef Bowls with Marinated Veggies and Nuoc Cham
description: Caramelized ground beef is an absolute game-changer in these Vietnamese-style meat and veggie bowls. Lime-pickled carrots and radishes add brightness and acidity to balance the sweet and savoury beef. Tangy and umami-packed nuoc cham completes the dish!
